<p class="definition">
    <strong>Volume</strong>
    <br><br>
    The amount of space that matter takes up.
</p>
<p class="definition">
    <strong>Expansion</strong>
    <br><br>
    When something gets larger and increases in volume
</p>
<p class="definition">
    <strong>Contraction</strong>
    <br><br>
    When something gets smaller and decreases in volume
</p>

